#

Seared Scallops with Lemon Butter Sauce

20 min
$25
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

shellfish

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freepaleolow-carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

seafoodquick mealgourmet

Description

Deliciously seared scallops drizzled with a rich lemon butter sauce, perfect for a quick gourmet meal.

Ingredients

  • scallops: 1 pound
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
